a pleasant surprise   // It means something positive happens in your life.

a complete disaster   // It describe an event where just didn't go well.

a total letdown       // It describe you really excited to something positive but it just a bad ending.

better that excited   //  It opposite a total letdown.

a real headache       // nothing go to my plan

a pain in the butt    // something you don't like do 

a real pleasure       // It describe something really make you happy

i can't help myself.  // a phrase used to describe something you do automatically without thinking.

to not cooperate      // an unwillingness to do what is expected.

to have the best intentions  // to plan to do something that needs to be done.